{"tid":1489732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全民孭袋！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T12:47:22.000Z","uid":6864,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f28a91651c20c34affe678f65ead4b9feb9178f","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"經過尋晚將軍澳恐襲，全香港人都睇到香港已經冇一個地方係安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住你唔加入衝突就冇事，而家對家嘅懦夫行為專向最弱最無力自保嘅青少年，特別女性出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，每個人以後出街都要有最低限度保護自己嘅能力，你身上孭個袋隨時救你一命！<br />\n<br />\n袋作為一件隨身死物，你可以揮動佢去格對方武器攻擊，仲可以保持同攻擊者嘅距離。 呢個方法肯定不完美，但總好過你用肉身硬食，係最低最即時嘅保護。"},{"pid":"b23fbe1abdbd5934281703d07fb84de9a8793389","tid":1489732,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"細golf bag, 加碌鐵， 全民高爾夫"},{"pid":"96b2ca045e062a9f929d257f17705be032051fa2","tid":1489732,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:53:41.000Z","msg":"要冷氣軍師唔好抽自衛武力後腳先，818遊行仲有人話邊個用武力就報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n斬人斬到今日，夠晒條件，點解仲未成立民間衛民隊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489680</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"475ba3e38900f3e64a77d37077b06db1750b4a8c","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"推，保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef807c4d849fc03e4e867695a0d7f25c7097013","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"保護自己"},{"pid":"a8a7251363442def13b973864ae03ec4efd3ff07","tid":1489732,"uid":276393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b23fbe1abdbd5934281703d07fb84de9a8793389","tid":1489732,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"細golf bag, 加碌鐵， 全民高爾夫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"你用會用<br />\n藏有攻擊性武器拉你<br />\n鬼叫唔撐d狗"},{"pid":"5724f01936ea3a16864fbab3d9eda664428629c7","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be25c2f4fbb0683c78ad6d5c77d1f125b05adc1","tid":1489732,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"背囊,搵d風嬲外套tee谷脹個袋<br />\n有咩危險都可以當盾擋一擋<br />\n當然保持一定距離係最安全"},{"pid":"64dbfa59fa8beac41211d4a3e1e435ee06eb96de","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"夜晚去貼牆嘅仔仔女女，已經多次受襲啦，要加強保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d55e3403deb255ca2286270309b1d36d143355","tid":1489732,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e0a99a66ebd8bc4a68fa81a7fef2313938239bf","tid":1489732,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"背囊入面可以放支象印暖水樽，0.48L，特點樽身係金屬，加強防禦力其實都可以用來扑鳩人。"},{"pid":"ab55b3408656bf2e574ade1df951264ca684ac28","tid":1489732,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"小弟去釣魚 拎住個魚竿袋十分輕便<br />\n入面放乜野 我控制唔到你<br />\n<img src=\"https://cf.shopee.tw/file/81c5834d65ffcc1afecb2cff0d46a1e6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf.shopee.tw%2Ffile%2F81c5834d65ffcc1afecb2cff0d46a1e6&h=a4eef5b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fdde31ed83b6d561770d5356c5ff4d352b84bd2","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"放咩都好，首先，要有個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算入面冇嘢都好，袋嘅布料係斬唔爛，可以fing幾下俾你爭取時間逃走或者等其他人幫手"},{"pid":"7b6ebbbce088932b06e384b63f85d657f471147b","tid":1489732,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"食飽推一推"}]}